headline: Dell (DELL) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of computer hardware and IT solutions company Dell (NYSE:DELL) fell 2.3% in the afternoon session after investors continued to react negatively to the company's third-quarter earnings guidance, which fell short of expectations.

headline: Heard on the Street Friday Recap: Cook's Day in Court
summary: A judge signaled she wishes to rule quickly on whether President Trump acted unlawfully in moving to fire Federal Reserve governor Lisa Cook. Judge Jia Cobb, a Biden appointee, didn’t issue any decisions from the bench during the two-hour hearing.
